---
title: Sweet Potato Massaman Curry with Spinach and Cilantro-Yogurt
description: A Thai dish with roots in Persia, this hearty and sweet potato curry is filling, a bit spicy and warm which will keep you full and cozy on a chilly night
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sweet-potato-massaman-curry-2b269142.jpg
